Kuch incident or yaad aa gaye...

Kitni fatti fatti rahi thi teri..
Ekdum abhiyanshu ke room gaya tha..
Fir panda se milna..Roz batana ki panda ab yeh bol raha ab yeh bol raha.

Tere naam k karan to teri sabne maari hi hai..Lekin sabne intentionally maari hai...

Raj Pala ki class me yeh kaam unintentionally ho gaya...South ke prof log sahi se naam nahi hi Lee paa rahe hote...Ya shyd north ke naam hard hote..Pta nahi kya reason hai..

Ayush ladha ko Ayush ledhaa..

Not A chut ...

Uss time to bach gaya..

2nd year me room to nahi mila saath.. Lekin me aapke room me ho pada rheta tha.. Or chintu ki crispy baate sunte rhete theâ€¦ chintu ke gaane â€œBe Inteha:- Esa karne me bada mazza aata hai..â€

Fir mene aapko ek baar 4 ball par 4 chakke bhi to maare the.. Yeht to yaad hi hogaâ€¦

text:
I saw you first time on 22nd July 2017, obviously the first day of IITK. We were in the same cab, And your unique voice can be recognized even in the crowded auditorium of 830 students.
Shuruaat me to koi baat hi nahi hui.. and 3rd year me saath me project mila, you have a dominating nature at that time, jesse tum baat baat par bolti thi ki "Tumse bola tha karne ko to kyu nahi kiya" and kaafi daata tumne uss project me mujhe. 
uske ek saal baad firse project partner ban gaye..ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ coincidentally... iss baar mujhe lag raha tha ki daant to nahi khaani tumhari.. to saara kaam kar diya time se..
CHE352 ke baad socha nahi tha kabhi itne ache dost ban paayenge..

"Maybe you have to know the darkness before you can appreciate the light." and you are much "brighter" and way more mature than I think earlier.

à¤ªà¥€à¤›à¥‡ à¤•à¤¿à¤¤à¤¨à¥€ à¤¯à¤¾à¤¦à¥‡ à¤¬à¥à¤¨ à¤—à¤¯à¤¾, à¤ªà¤¤à¤¾ à¤¹à¥€ à¤¨à¤¾ à¤šà¤²à¤¾ !!""
